{"tid":743542,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"陶傑同性經驗之談：「未試過，人生係唔算 complete（完整）。」","createTime":"2018-07-15T13:15:55.000Z","updateTime":"2018-07-15T18:15:06.000Z","uid":1426,"like":13,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"fee3ca3c2087b65ebf3ea27b982d4328e5b52cbd","tid":743542,"uid":1426,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-15T13:15:55.000Z","msg":"何謂人生的最高境界？原來並非有錢、有地位、有學識，而係乜都試過玩過先至堅。對於同性戀這個敏感話題，才子陶傑經驗之談：「未試過，人生係唔算 complete（完整）。」他不是雙性戀，只是曾經年少輕狂。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n男男性愛經歷<br />\n<br />\n很多人對同性戀戴上有色眼鏡，尤其身為父母或長輩，但在才子眼中同性戀和異性戀無差別。「依家係 21世紀，好多人都仲好封閉。我覺得喺性愛方面未試過同性戀，人生係唔算 complete（完整）。（你試過？）當年我讀嗰間寄宿學校係男校，有咩未試過，不過我同對方就冇感情嘅。（你係 1〔男方〕定 0〔女方〕？）我當然係做『 1』啦！」原來不單止要 never pay for sex，可以不分男女才是最高境界。"},{"pid":"093373a521001c9ddd6dd5ab8790abe3a3d20abc","tid":743542,"uid":141917,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-15T13:18:54.000Z","msg":"假膠"},{"pid":"6f3ef94d4e9ad7823c4e2395f698a456956a6a4d","tid":743542,"uid":1426,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"093373a521001c9ddd6dd5ab8790abe3a3d20abc","tid":743542,"uid":141917,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-15T13:18:54.000Z","msg":"假膠"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-15T13:19:48.000Z","msg":"夠膽出黎互含!"},{"pid":"f11404f87e1135d69962292bdb1ae6629cfed119","tid":743542,"uid":55011,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-15T13:20:46.000Z","msg":"咁我唔完整都夠啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/37.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f97a1c86c76713d9f0dbace3196b3902e9bad03e","tid":743542,"uid":143284,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-15T13:20:48.000Z","msg":"why lau g 呢排開咁多gay po"},{"pid":"d2d62871a948fdda770bb31e810c288fa13b9985","tid":743542,"uid":4586,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-15T13:21:46.000Z","msg":"幾時放監"},{"pid":"838f5357a758691186d95a62d1867f07e363d78d","tid":743542,"uid":155137,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-15T14:07:40.00